    • addLayer

      private static void addLayer() throws Exception
      Adds a new layer to the map by parsing a selected TXT file. Uses TXTFileParser.getTXTFile(File) for parsing selected file and Styles.chooseStyle(javax.swing.JFrame) for obtaining a selected style
      Throws:
      Exception - if the file selection, validation or parsing fails.

    • showRemoveLayerMenu

      Throws:
